conditions are generally safe, but if you are traveling in steep terrain, there are still a few things to watch for. At the top of steep chutes and couloirs, you may find recent deposits of drifted snow. Triggering a small avalanche in this drifted snow could have serious consequences if you are swept off your feet in extreme terrain. Also watch for any recent snow warming under Thursday\u2019s strong sun. The newest snow can easily shed on top of shallowly buried crusts.<\/p>"}]},"terrainAndTravelAdvice":{"days":[[],[],[]]},"communication":{"headline":"","sms":""},"media":{"Images":[{"id":"1ad58631-a3e4-45f5-bb35-deb96024723c","url":"http:\/\/res.cloudinary.com\/dozsqvbas\/image\/upload\/v1778189185\/AvIDfx\/jrzi56dlz3xiapqskdhg.webp","width":350,"height":263,"credit":"","caption":"<p>Wet avalanches like this one in the Silver Couloir on Buffalo Mountain on May 5th are possible on Friday and through the weekend. Avoid very steep slopes where the snow feels wet.<\/p>","tag":"avalanche","altText":"wet avy","dateTaken":"2026-05-05T21:26:29.689Z","isArchived":false},{"id":"48ed1e15-068c-4ba9-9ac3-c451da6ce46e","url":"http:\/\/res.cloudinary.com\/dozsqvbas\/image\/upload\/v1778097720\/AvIDfx\/ondd0oqzpjjh8tlo59gy.webp","width":2500,"height":1875,"credit":"","caption":"<p>Look for and avoid stiff wind-drifted slabs like this one right below a ridgeline. <\/p>","tag":"avalanche","altText":"Wind drifted slab avalanche below a ridgeline","dateTaken":"2026-04-15T19:20:44Z","isArchived":false},{"id":"98e3252a-c3a9-4827-a471-2e56831f6e1a","url":"http:\/\/res.cloudinary.com\/dozsqvbas\/image\/upload\/v1777665910\/AvIDfx\/unbpaur7n870ic0jcrpq.webp","width":1204,"height":1600,"credit":"","caption":"<p>Avalanches will be easier to trigger on slopes with more than about eight inches of snow.<\/p>","tag":"avalanche","altText":"Rollerballs near rocks. ","dateTaken":"2026-04-28T20:09:20.179Z","isArchived":false}]},"dangerRatings":{"days":[{"position":1,"alp":"low","tln":"low","btl":"low","date":"2026-05-08T22:30:00Z"},{"position":2,"alp":"low","tln":"low","btl":"low","date":"2026-05-09T22:30:00Z"},{"position":3,"alp":"low","tln":"low","btl":"low","date":"2026-05-10T22:30:00Z"}]},"avalancheProblems":{"days":[[],[],[]]}}]